# GraphQL Explorer — environment configuration
#
# VITE_GRAPHQL_URL is the SINGLE knob that points the app at the LMDB2GraphQL lens.
# It is the only place a base URL is configured at runtime (resolved in
# src/transport/config.ts). Default is loopback; /ready and /health are derived
# from the same origin.
#
# SECURITY (V14): the lens is an UNAUTHENTICATED, full-introspection, wildcard-CORS,
# read-only API. v1 is local-dev only — keep this on loopback. Overriding it to a
# public/untrusted host means the app sends queries to, and trusts responses from,
# that origin. Any wider exposure needs a gateway (auth/rate-limit/TLS) — out of scope.
VITE_GRAPHQL_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8080/graphql
